document_data.History:
Following the Spellplague many of the [[Gond]] worshipers from the destroyed nation of [[Lantan]] gathered in this region to explore the ruins of ancient civilizations that had been pushed to the surface in the wake of the Underchasm's creation. They were known to be working alongside [[gold dwarves]] in this effort and used many salvage companies.{{Cite dragon/403/Gond's Way: Artificers of the Realms|2}}

Eventually, the Deep Lords allowed the the Gondsmen to construct a permanent residence in the area. The subsequent construction of a new temple to their god was led by [[Cavandro the Cunning]].

